name: North Central DPH
tweet: When you bring your #Thanksgiving groceries home, separate raw meat, poultry, seafood and eggs from other foods in the refrigerator. Place them in containers or sealed plastic bags on the bottom shelf of the refrigerator. #TheStoryOfYourDinner  https://t.co/dtY2qvX19N
